title: Thomasch Watch Face
summary: An excellent handcrafted watch face for Android Wear, made by Thomasch Sweden.
description: Thomasch Sweden presents its first watch face for Android Wear. It has a clean dark analog theme, without too many bloated items attached. It's a typical classic watch face that is suitable for everyone.This quality watch face is handcrafted with real computer tools of high quality. However, if you happen to find a bug, please contact us! We'll fix it as soon as possible.It's compatible with both square and round Android Wear watches with version 5.0 or higher.
descriptionHTML:
Thomasch Sweden presents its first watch face for Android Wear. It has a clean dark analog theme, without too many bloated items attached. It's a typical classic watch face that is suitable for everyone.

This quality watch face is handcrafted with real computer tools of high quality. However, if you happen to find a bug, please contact us! We'll fix it as soon as possible.

It's compatible with both square and round Android Wear watches with version 5.0 or higher.
